Bobertron got Mantella's massage. He went into the command room of the Destron ship and looked around for the Red button. Pantron came in after him and helped in the search.


"Where is it?" Bobertron asked.


"I've found it!" Pantron replied, he tried pushing it but nothing hapened. Then Bobertron came over and pushed it, there were lots of whirring sounds coming from the ship....
